==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: ān jiā lì yè
===Etymology===
Literally: settle down with a family and build a career
*[[安]]-> [[安置]]
*[[家]]-> [[家庭]]
*[[立]]-> [[建立]]
*[[業]]/[[业]]-> [[事業]], [[事业]]


===Idiom===
'''[[安]][[家]][[立]][[業]]'''
#  to settle down
===Alternate forms===
[[安家立业]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
